text: Browns have dealt with quarterback injuries throughout training camp. text:

Lions signed OL Gunner Britton, OL Keaton Sutherland, TE Gunnar Oakes and RB Deon Jackson.

author: AdamSchefter
text:
Colts veteran RB Salvon Ahmed, who was taken down by a defender with an illegal hip-drop tackle, suffered a season-ending ankle injury, per me and @HolderStephen.

Colts are signing former Dolphins RB Nate Noel.

colts veteran rb salvon ahmed, who was taken down by a defender with an illegal hip-drop tackle, suffered a season-ending ankle injury, per me and @holderstephen.

colts are signing former dolphins rb nate noel.

author: AdamSchefter
text:
Cowboys placed guard Rob Jones on season-ending injured reserve due to a broken bone in his neck. 

Cowboys also signed RB Malik Davis.

text: On the injury front, WR Wan’Dale Robinson went down with a leg issue earlier. Has been riding the bike and flexing his leg while watching practice. No major alarms there. WR Bryce Ford-Wheaton, a special-teams contributor, was carted off minutes ago. That one didn’t look great.

author: AdamSchefter
text:
Back in March, the Eagles traded safety C.J. Gardner-Johnson to the Houston Texans in exchange for offensive guard Kenyon Green.

Both players were injured today. Gardner-Johnson left practice with a knee injury, Green left tonight’s game with a wrist injury.

both players were injured today. gardner-johnson left practice with a knee injury, green left tonight’s game with a wrist injury.

author: FieldYates
text:
After trading Deebo Samuel and with Brandon Aiyuk’s return date from a knee injury uncertain, the Niners would be very thin in a world without Jauan Jennings.

When Jennings has gotten a chance to play extensively, he’s almost always balled out.

text:

DT Kevin Givens suffered a pec injury and will be out “a while”, per Shanahan.
